name: The Bunker Institute for the Undead Studies

metadata.name: Engagooooorrrr
metadata.description: This time our fearless research team has gone all in, trying to uncover the mysterious reason why Zombies just can't seem to put their phones down. It appears that these undead beings are utterly obsessed with the captivating realm of Crypto Twitter. But why, you ask? Well, we're as clueless as a goldfish with short-term memory loss. However, we do have some interesting findings to share! As it turns out, ever since our team embarked on this peculiar investigation, our productivity has taken a nosedive straight into the void. But hey, at least now we can proudly say that we've become the trendiest bunch of brain-craving researchers in the lab!
